text: Lorient or L'Orient may refer to: *Lorient, a town in Brittany, France **FC Lorient, a French professional football league team *Lorient, Saint Barthélemy *L'Orient, Switzerland, a village forming part of the municipality of Le Chenit in Vaud, Switzerland *French ship L'Orient (1791), a French warship, sunk at the Battle of the Nile *Raid on Lorient, a 1746 British attempt to capture the town during the War of the Austrian Succession == See also == * Orient (disambiguation)
title: Lorient (disambiguation)
